text:
James Corden Breaks Down 'Britney Ever After' And It Is Hysterical (WATCH) posted by Alex Gervasi - 
"Britney Ever After" aired on Lifetime over the weekend and James Corden decided to watch it. 
His thoughts on the Britney Spears biopic are absolutely hilarious. Check them out above. Tweets by @AlexontheMic What's up? I'm Alex! So I guess I'll tell you a little bit about myself. I grew up in South Jersey (10 minutes from Philly) and went to school a few minutes from Lexington, Kentucky. Growing up I always wanted to be on the air. What's better than talking about and listening to music for a living? Sounds like a pretty good job to me. I'm here to to provide some good music for your ears and keep you informed on all the latest things happening around here. Sound good? Follow me on Twitter/Instagram: @alexonthemic Contact
